./pub-sub


Answers:
--------

Q: What is the message publish algorithm complexity in big-O notation?
A: O(n) in the subscriber count.

Q: What is the message poll algorithm complexity in big-O notation?
A: O(log n) in the subscriber count, worst case O(n) in the count of the
messages.

Q: What is the memory (space) complexity in big-O notation for the algorithm?
A: O(n).
